@M_KOJO_MESSAGE_MARKCNG_K142
;このままだと地の文が表示されません
;地の文を表示したい方は、下記のコメントアウトを削除して下さい
;Pain Mark
;苦痛刻印
IF TFLAG:22 == 1
	PRINTFORML 「Ow!」
	PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% glares at you.
	PRINTFORMW 「Whaddya think this is, a Danmaku match?!」
ELSEIF TFLAG:22 == 2
	PRINTFORMW 「Kh!」
	PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grits %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% teeth.
	PRINTFORML 「Look, being a youkai doesn't mean I can't feel pain.」
	PRINTFORMW 「So you'd better knock it off before I hurt you back.」
ELSEIF TFLAG:22 == 3
	PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% screams in pain.
	PRINTFORMW 「Why?! How?!」
	PRINTFORMDW She skitters away from you. %HIS_HER([[百々世]],1)% eyes are wide with fear and shock, and tears are streaming down %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% face.
	PRINTFORML 「Look, I dunno how you're doing this, or what I did to piss you off...」
	PRINTFORMW 「But I'm sorry, okay?! Just stop hurting me!」
	PRINTFORMW 「Please...」
	PRINTFORMW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% hugs %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% knees to %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% chest and looks at you pitifully.
ENDIF

